{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7fddaba8fc","title":"粉碎蒋军进攻热东冀东等地的部署","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d0da3f9ad8","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":28,"articleId":"7fddaba8fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0df6449cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎蒋军进攻热东冀东等地的部署口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc"},{"id":"46c96b8693","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月28日）程、李，并告楚、萧、刘P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc"},{"id":"dd8760d9d2","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）蒋军进攻计划是先攻热东、冀东及长城线，以一部向承德伴攻，侯热东、冀东及长城线得手后，再以全力攻承德。（二）你们应动员全力在热东、鑫东及长城线上打击与消耗敌人，退淄敌人前进时间；对伴攻承德之敌必须给以有力回击以阻止之。（三）上述斗争时间愈延长愈对我先取大同再取平汉“之作战计划有利","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc"},{"id":"8c191dfdeb","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc"},{"id":"bf065c0086","type":"paragraph","text":"未俭F11这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给翼热辽军区司令员兼政治委员程子华和副司令员李运昌的电报。2]爱、萧、刘，指凝荣臻、萧克、刘澜涛，当时分别任晋察冀军区司令员兼政治委员、副司令员和副政治委员。[3]热东，指当时热河（旧省名，辖今河北省东北部、辽宁省西南部和内蒙古自治区东南部地区，1955年撤销）的东部地区","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc"}],"page":{"id":"6169c4825b","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7fddaba8fc","start":101,"end":101}}}},"__N_SSG":true}